eOfFire:null,shots:null,projectiles:null},effects:["+50 HP, +4 DEF, +3 DEX","Keyper’s Trickery: Releases a barrage of 10 keys to hinder opponents On Taking Damage: 10% chance to create key nova Key Damage: 100 Key Bullet Speed: 8.5 tiles/second Key Range: 4.25 tiles Key Effect: Slowed for 2s, Exposed for 4s Cooldown: 5 seconds"],usableClasses:[],dropsFrom:[],notes:[],sourceUrl:"https://www.realmeye.com/wiki/crystal-key",spriteUrl:"",icon:""},{id:"crystal-mace",name:"Crystal Mace",slug:"crystal-mace",category:"abilities",subCategory:"maces",sprite:"/items/crystal-mace.png",itemType:"Mace",tier:"UT",bagType:"White",soulbound:!1,fameBonus:"7%",feedPower:900,description:"Notes Along with the Stonemould Mace, this is currently only one of two maces to ignore the defense of its target, making it a solid choice for cracking high-DEF enemies that would normally shrug off other summons. While its total base damage is higher than many other maces, the steeds’ reliance on hitting all their (individually weaker) shots crimps its DPS somewhat, especially against enemies with low DEF that would generally take more damage from other maces.",stats:{damage:"50–70 (average: 60)",range:"5 tiles",rateOfFire:null,shots:"5",projectiles:"5"},effects:["+4 SPD, +4 WIS","Shots pass through obstacles Ignores defense of target"],usableClasses:[],dropsFrom:["Crystal Prisoner","Mighty Quest Chest"],notes:[],sourceUrl:"https://www.realmeye.com/wiki/crystal-mace",spriteUrl:"",icon:""},{id:"crystal-shield",name:"Crystal Shield",slug:"crystal-shield",category:"abilities",subCategory:"shields",sprite:"/items/crystal-shield.png",itemType:"Shield",tier:"UT",bagType:"White",soulbound:!0,fameBonus:"7%",feedPower:950,description:"Notes A bizarre and completely unique shield that functions similarly to a Ninja star.",stats:{damage:null,range:null,rateOfFire:null,shots:null,projectiles:null},effects:["+10 DEF, +40 HP, -10 SPD","While Armored: On taking damage, fire a shot in retaliation. While Armored: On taking 30 or more damage, heal 10 HP."],usableClasses:[],dropsFrom:["Crystal Worm Mother","Crystallized Epic Quest Chest"],notes:[],sourceUrl:"https://www.realmeye.com/wiki/crystal-shield",spriteUrl:"",icon:""},{id:"crystal-sword",name:"Crystal Sword",slug:"crystal-sword",sprite:"/items/crystal-sword.png",itemType:"Sword",tier:"UT",bagType:"White",soulbound:!1,fameBonus:"5%",feedPower:600,description:"Notes The Crystal Sword is a utility weapon with the highest practical range of non-vanity swords, one tile higher than tiered options. The Pixie-Enchanted Sword and Divinity’s beams have higher range but do not hit all shots at that range. It exchanges damage in the process, being even weaker than the T8 Ravenheart Sword. Despite being noticably weaker, CSword allows players to more easily hit dangerous-to-approach enemies like Oryx the Mad God 2.",stats:{damage:"195–225 (average: 210)",range:"4.5 tiles",rateOfFire:null,shots:"1",projectiles:"1"},effects:[],usableClasses:["Warrior","Knight","Paladin"],dropsFrom:["Crystal Prisoner"],notes:[],sourceUrl:"https://www.realmeye.com/wiki/crystal-sword",category:"swords",subCategory:"",spriteUrl:"",icon:""},{id:"crystal-wand",name:"Crystal Wand",slug:"crystal-wand",sprite:"/items/crystal-wand.png",itemType:"Wand",tier:"UT",bagType:"White",soulbound:!1,fameBonus:"5%",feedPower:700,description:"Notes This wand’s damage ignores defense, making it good for fighting enemies/bosses with high amounts of defense, or those protected with the Armored status effect. Examples include the Avatar of the Forgotten King, the Puppet Master, the Stone Guardians, and the Tormented Golem. One of the best places to use this wand is in the Parasite Chambers, as the boss of this dungeon has 5,000 defense until it is armor broken.",stats:{damage:"105–150 (average: 127.5)",range:"9 tiles",rateOfFire:"110%",shots:"1",projectiles:"1"},effects:["Shots hit multiple targets Ignores defense of target"],usableClasses:["Priest","Sorcerer","Summoner"],dropsFro